product design and manufacturing club pdmc stanford graduate school of business the pdmc is committed to bridging disciplines helping its members and partners envision realize and sustain remarkable products and experiences we bring together design manufacturing business at the stanford graduate school of business among the programs and events it sponsors the pdmc organizes the annual cool product expo one of the largest student run conferences at stanford university the cpx is a showcase of innovative companies and products at the intersection of manufacturing design and cool it invites exhibitors from a variety of industries that practice innovation by way of design function and or technology drawing 1300 attendees from students to families to vcs learn more about the cpx co presidents amanda boaz laura jones & tom nguyen cfo andii davis for more information about the pdmc email pdm_leadership at gsb dot stanford dot edu the pdmc is sponsored by the product realization network at stanford and the stanford graduate school of business
